Interface ModifiableRealmIdentityIterator

    public interface ModifiableRealmIdentityIterator
extends java.util.Iterator<ModifiableRealmIdentity>, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    An iterator over realm identities. The iterator should be closed in order to release any associated resources.
